quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  2,26,"Hobane Ruri Allah ha a khese ho sebelisa papiso le ha e se e le ea monoang. Bakholoang ba ea tseba hore seo ke ‘nete etsoang ho Mong`a bona; empa ba khesang tumelo bona ba re: “e be Allah U bolelang ka papiso ee?” Allah U khelositse ba ba ngata ka eona, a tataisa ba bangata ka eona; o khelositse feela ba khopo"
  2,27,"Haele ba robang selekane sa Allah kamor’a hoba se theoe, ba bile ba arola seo Allah A laetseng hore se kopangoe, le hona ho fehla merusu lefats’eng: bao ke ba lahlehetsoeng"
  2,28,"Le latola joang tumelo ho `Mopi(Allah) empa le ne le hloka bophelo, a le neha bophelo! O tla le neha lefu, a be a le nehe bophelo hape; hobane poelo ea lona e ho Eena"
  2,29,Ke Eena Ea le hloletseng tsohle tse holima lefats’eng. Ho feta moo tsebo ea Hae e okamela popong ea maholimo. O fane ka taelo le tlhoeko maholimong a supileng; o nale tsebo e phetahetseng ho tsohle
  2,30,"Elelloang Mong`a lona A re ho manyeloi: « ke tla bopa moemeli lefats›eng,» manyeloi a re: « na o ka beha ea tla baka likotsi le hona ho tsolla mali lefats›eng, empa rona re ntse re keteka lithoriso tsa hau le hona ho o tlotlisa? “eaba Allah U re: “Ruri ke tseba seo le sa se tsebeng.”"
  2,31,"Allah U ruta Adama mabitso a lintho tsohle, a libeha ka pela manyeloi, a re: “mpolelleng mabitso a tsena haeba le na le ‘nete.”"
  2,32,"Manyeloi a re: “tlotla e ke e be ho Uena! Rona ha re na tsebo haese seo o re rutileng sona. Hobane ke Uena, Uena feela ea tsebang, Ea Seli.”"
  2,33,"Allah A re: “Adama! ba bolelle mabitso a tsona,” e itse hoba a ba bolella mabitso a tsona, Allah A re: “na ha ke ea bolela hore ke tseba liphiri tsa maholimo le lefats’e? Etsoe ke tseba tseo le li pepesang le tseo le li patang.”"
  2,34,"Elelloang Ra Re ho manyeloi: “ikokobetseng kapel’a Adama,” ba ile ba inama haese ibliss (satane). O ile a nyefola ka boikhohomoso, ea eba oa pele mohana-tumelo"
  2,35,"Ra re: “Adama lula le mosali oa hau serapeng, le be le je litholoana ka bolokolohi tse teng serapeng seo; empa le se atamele haufi le sefate sena, ho seng joalo le tlababaetsa- phoso.”"
  2,36,"Eaba satane o ba ekela ho theoha moo, ba tsoa serapeng sa boiketlo seo ba neng ba le ho sona; ba re: “theohang, mong le mong ka bora pakeng tsa lona! Lefats’e e tlaba bolulo ba lona le boiphiliso ha nakoana"
  2,37,"Adama a amohela mantsoe a ts’enolo a tsoang ho Mong`a hae, eaba Allah U retellehela ka ho eena. Hobane Ruri Allah U reteleha-khafetsa, etsoe o tletse mohau"
  2,38,"Ra re: “theohang kaofela ha lona, empa Ruri ke tla le romella tataiso e tsoang ho ‘Na; ba tla latela tataiso ea Ka ba ke ke ba eba le ts’abo kapa eona mesarelo"
  2,39,"Empa haele bo tlhoka-tumelo, ba bile ba nyefola lits’enolo tsa rona, Ruri bao ke balekane ba mollo. ba tla phela moo.”"
  2,40,"Bana ba Israele! Hopolang molemo oo ke le sitsitseng ka oona, le be le phethise selekane sa lona, etsoe le ‘Na (Allah) ke tla se phethisa, le se ts’abe mong kantle ho `Na"
  2,41,"Le lumele ho se ke se senotseng se tihisang ts`enolo e teng ho lona, le se be ba pele ho nyefola tumelo teng, le ho rekisa ka lits’enolo tsa ka ka thekoana e eisehang; le be le ts`abo ho ‘na, ke inots`i"
  2,42,"Le se ribehe ‹nete ka bohata, kapa la pata ‹nete le tseba"
  2,43,"Tsitlallelang thapelong, pheellang ho fana ka linyehelo, inamisang lihlooho le ba inamang thapelong"